dc_title_s: LiDAR-Derived Tiled DEM for Rusk County, WI 2011
dc_description_s: This data represents a LiDAR-derived tiled Digital Surface Model (DSM) for Rusk County, Wisconsin in 2011. A Digital Surface Model captures both the natural and built/artificial features of the environment. This dataset contains individual files available for download consisting of smaller tiled geographic areas over the extent of an entire county.
uw_supplemental_s: This data is also available as a series of tiles to enable downloads of smaller, more specific areas within the county. To access the tiled data, please visit: https://www.sco.wisc.edu/scoapps/lidar/tile-search/?layer=rusk
